Basic Tailoring:<br>
<br>
First, train 1 point at the trainer.  20pts if you want, but it is not necessary.  Make sure you have a small or large sewing kit.  Put the ingredients in the sewing kit and click combine.<br>
<br>
1-15 - Combine 2 non-stacked spiderling silks to make silk thread.  No-fail combine.  OR  get a skinning knife at bazaar and combine it with a MQ hide to make a LQ hide.   Also no-fail, and you get the knife back.<br>
<br>
16-26 - Patchwork Armor.  1 ruined bear, cat, or wolf pelt and a pattern.  Stick with mask or gorget.  Patterns can be bought everywhere.<br>
<br>
